currentDoc:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

currentSuggestions.original: "I found it in the ground, like everyone else does," said the pig.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "I found it in the ground, like everyone else does," said the pig.

currentSuggestions.original: "I can't tell you or it wouldn't be a secret anymore," said the 92nd little pig.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "I can't tell you or it wouldn't be a secret anymore," said the 92nd little pig.

currentSuggestions.original: The pig replied, "You don't want to know."
currentSuggestions.trimmed: The pig replied, "You don't want to know."

currentSuggestions.original: "I found it in the trash," said the 92nd little pig.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "I found it in the trash," said the 92nd little pig.

currentSuggestions.original: "In my house," replied the little pig.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "In my house," replied the little pig.

ops.insert: "In my house," replied the little pig.

currentSuggestions.original: "Can I come in and look at it?" the wolf asked.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "Can I come in and look at it?" the wolf asked.

currentSuggestions.original: He stormed up to the door and huffed and puffed until he blew the house down.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: He stormed up to the door and huffed and puffed until he blew the house down.

currentSuggestions.original: Maybe the pigs had built it with magic.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Maybe the pigs had built it with magic.

currentSuggestions.original: Maybe the pig had a black-market uranium dealer.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Maybe the pig had a black-market uranium dealer.

ops.insert: "Can I come in and look at it?" the wolf asked.

currentSuggestions.original: Inside the wolf saw that the little pig was right, it was a magic house.

currentSuggestions.original: The pig took him downstairs and showed him a pile of uranium ore.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: The pig took him downstairs and showed him a pile of uranium ore.
